metadata.name: ✶ somewhere nice ✶
metadata.description:
This piece is dedicated to my two sweet precious holland lop.

At night, after I'm tired from staring at drawing screen for a while, I turn off the lights and sit in my rabbit pen. Babe and Yuzu, my two little girls will come to me, asking for treats and petting. It is an amazing recharge. Sometimes, I imagine we would travel together, 

..to somewhere nice.
